### Create Staff
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/staff/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Duck",
  "email": "john.duck@staff.com",
  "role": "Mechanic",
  "active": true
}

### Create Super Admin (Full Module Access)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/staff/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Super Admin",
  "username": "admin",
  "role": "Admin",
  "active": true,
  "permissions": ["Appointments", "Service Tracking", "Invoices", "Customers", "Vehicles", "Service Types", "Staff"]
}

### Get All Staff
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/staff/

### Get Staff with Search
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/staff/?search=john&active=true

### Get Staff by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/staff/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Update Staff
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/v1/staff/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "john.doe.updated@staff.com",
  "role": "Senior Mechanic",
  "active": true
}

### Delete Staff
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/staff/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000